<section id="section-6">
    <h2>TELL YOUR STORY</h2>
    <div>
        <p>Come From Away shares the stories of over 7,000 people diverted to Gander, we know there are many more
            stories to be shared from Plane People around the world.
        </p>

        <p>Tell us your story from September 11, 2001 to help us honor all those who come from away and pin your story
            to the map.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div id="form">
        <h1>TELL YOUR STORY FORM</h1>
        <form action="POST">
            <h4>Name</h4>
            <input type="text">
        </form>
        <form action="POST">
            <h4>Email</h4>
            <input type="text">
        </form>
        <form action="POST">
            <h4>Location (City,State)</h4>
            <input type="text">
        </form>
        <h4>Were you on a flight that was forced to land on 9/11?</h4>
        <button>Yes</button>
        <button>No</button>
        <h4>Did you land in or around Gander, Newfoundland?</h4>
        <button>Yes</button>
        <button>No</button>
        <form action="POST">
            <h4>Share your sttory of your experience the week of 9/11:</h4>
            <h5>(300 character limit)</h5>
            <input type="text" id="ip1">
        </form>
        <form action="POST">
            <h4>Tell us how you continue to honor what you found. Do you keep in touch with anyone you met or have you
                made any return visits since 2001?</h4>
            <h5>(300 character limit)</h5>
            <input type="text" id="ip2">
        </form>
        <button>SUBMIT</button>
    </div>
</section>